title: Element Clippings 004 - Minneapolis, MN
description:
Element team riders Evan Smith, Greyson Fletcher, Nick Garcia and Brandon Westgate headed to Minneapolis for the weekend stopping by Familia HQ and 3rd Lair skate parks. 

Filmed by Marc Falkenstien and Peter Jones
